      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "UNMATCH / DELETE STATEMENT:\n1. Reverse bank_recon JVs\n2. Delete BankTransactionInvoice → recalc invoice amount_paid\n3. Delete BankTransactionClaim → claim payment_status → unpaid\n4. Clear matched_sales_invoice_id → update sales invoice\n5. Delete legacy auto-created Payments + PaymentReceipts\n6. recon_status → unmatched (or delete if statement deleted)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
