    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "text_partial",
      "x": 545,
      "y": 738,
      "width": 490,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "SPECIAL CASES:\n• Partial match: 1 bank txn → multiple invoices/claims\n  Each creates BankTransactionInvoice/Claim with allocation amount\n  Amber badge when total allocated < bank txn amount\n• Multi-invoice selection: grouped by supplier, collapsible cards\n• Exclude: recon_status = 'excluded' (skip, no JV)\n• RE-MATCH button: re-runs 4-pass on all unmatched txns\n• Bank GL prerequisite: BankAccount.gl_account_id REQUIRED",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
