      "originalText": "SPECIAL CASES:\n• Partial match: 1 bank txn → multiple invoices/claims\n  Each creates BankTransactionInvoice/Claim with allocation amount\n  Amber badge when total allocated < bank txn amount\n• Multi-invoice selection: grouped by supplier, collapsible cards\n• Exclude: recon_status = 'excluded' (skip, no JV)\n• RE-MATCH button: re-runs 4-pass on all unmatched txns\n• Bank GL prerequisite: BankAccount.gl_account_id REQUIRED",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
